OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud and
OL,6,Fsome patchy rain clearing from
OL,7,Fsoutheast England, then chilly with
OL,8,Fclear periods in the south this
OL,9,Fevening. However, blustery showers in
OL,10,Fthe northwest becoming increasingly
OL,11,Fwidespread overnight, some heavy and
OL,12,Fpossibly thundery. Limited frost as
OL,13,Fwinds strengthen.
OL,14,
OL,15,CWednesday:FA mix of sunshine and
OL,16,Fshowers across the UK. Some of the
OL,17,Fshowers heavy with hail and thunder,
OL,18,Feven some wintriness over the Scottish
OL,19,Fmountains. Brisk and chilly
OL,20,Fnorthwesterly winds.
